UMboweni uthe ubhiya uzonyuka ngo-8 cents, iwayini ngo-14 cents, iwayini elihlohlozayo ngo-61 cents, ugologo ngoR2.89. Iphakethe likagwayi i-20 lizonyuka ngo-74 cents, isigazu ngoR6.73. Ijuba ngeke linyuke. Kulokhu uMboweni uthe bazoqala ukufaka intela kulezo zinto ezihlobene nogwayi noma ezishiswayo bese ziyabhenywa. “Ugwayi ophafuzwa ngogesi (electronic cigarettes) wona bekungakhishwa ntela ngawo kodwa manje sekuzoshintsha lokho,” kusho uMboweni. Kusukela ngo-2021 uhulumeni uzobe esefaka intela kulo gwayi ojwayele ukubheywa abadla izambane likapondo. Ne-hubble bubble nayo kuthiwa isizofakwa intela kusukela ngo-2021. I-hubble ijwayele ukubhenywa ezindaweni zobumnandi, inamapayipi ekufuquzwa ngawo intuthu. Ucwazi nawo uMboweni uthe uzofakwa intela ka-25 cents kusuka ngo-Ephreli nonyaka. IRandi livele ladlo-ndlobala ngemuva kwalesi sabelo sikaMboweni njengoba kuqale usuku lintenga lase liyaqina lahlala kuR15.09.